These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, canasta
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff
City: nizza, rome
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, white
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
2. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
3. the aristoff-smoker is not the person who growslily##6
4. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
5. the person traveling to rome is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
6. the person who likes white is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
7. the owner of the goldfish is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Game      | canasta   | monopoly      |
| Pet          | lizard | goldfish   |
| Cigar         | aristoff    | tiparillo |
| City           | nizza     | rome    |
| Flower   | begonia    | lily       |
| Color   | lavender    | white        |
| Sport     | tennis     | volleyball        |

